# Cloudflare SSL 模式建议「完全(严格)」，Tunnel 提供端到端加密
http://{{DOMAIN}}:{{PORT}} {
    handle_path /wg* {
        reverse_proxy wg-easy:51821 {
            header_up Host {http.reverse_proxy.upstream.host}
            header_up X-Forwarded-For {remote_host}
        }
    }

    handle {
        root * /var/www/blog
        file_server
        encode gzip
    }
}
